sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Endpoint
    participant Mediator
    participant Validator
    participant Handler
    participant QuotaService
    participant Domain as UserLibraryEntry
    participant DB as Database
    participant Events

    Client->>Endpoint: POST /api/v1/library/games/{gameId}
    Note right of Client: Add game to library

    Endpoint->>Endpoint: Extract gameId from route
    Endpoint->>Endpoint: Create AddGameToLibraryCommand

    Endpoint->>Mediator: Send(AddGameToLibraryCommand)

    Mediator->>Validator: Validate(command)
    Validator->>Validator: Check gameId is valid GUID
    Validator->>DB: Verify game exists
    DB-->>Validator: Game found ✓
    Validator->>Mediator: Validation passed ✓

    Mediator->>Handler: Handle(command)

    Handler->>DB: Check duplicate entry
    DB-->>Handler: Not exists ✓

    Handler->>QuotaService: CheckQuota(userId)
    QuotaService->>DB: Get user tier + current count
    DB-->>QuotaService: Free tier: 7/10 games
    QuotaService-->>Handler: Quota available ✓

    Handler->>Domain: UserLibraryEntry.Create(userId, gameId)
    Domain->>Domain: Set AddedAt = UtcNow
    Domain->>Domain: Set TimesPlayed = 0
    Domain->>Events: Raise GameAddedToLibraryEvent

    Handler->>DB: SaveAsync(entry)
    DB-->>Handler: Entry saved ✓

    Handler->>Events: Publish GameAddedToLibraryEvent

    Handler-->>Mediator: UserLibraryEntryDto
    Mediator-->>Endpoint: UserLibraryEntryDto

    Endpoint-->>Client: 201 Created
    Note left of Client: {entryId, gameId, addedAt}
